{"tid":1382995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警軍備已升級！！！","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:12:40.000Z","uid":94441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbfbd4a6e06b614c5d47ccf618d30ae8e1efabf3","tid":1382995,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"//今次所使用嘅「MP-4-R3」則屬於多頭彈，#每發子彈內藏有三顆橡膠彈。<br />\n<br />\n根據生產商的指引，「MP-4-R3」唔可以直接瞄準對方身體，而應該射擊目標前近距離的地面，以反彈擊中目標（skip fired toward the subjects），並警告一旦喺短距離直接射擊對方身體，則會重傷或死亡。由於「MP-4-R3」具有爆破性，一旦打中，則會出現爆炸性傷口（blast or crush-type injuries ），而且指引警告唔可以打到易燃物料或明火之上。但見警方上環及元朗鎮壓期間多次瞄準示威者平射，明顯違反相關武器指引。<br />\n<br />\n警方甚至連催淚彈都「升級」咗，由「Skat Shell 37 mm Multiple Projectile Round CS」變成「MP-6M5-CS」。兩間公司講到明會導致物件起火，唔可以向屋頂或者其他有火災危險嘅地方發射；亦唔可以直接向人發射，否則可以導致嚴重受傷，甚至死亡。不過香港警察就喺元朗打中老人院簷蓬，喺上環打中永安招牌平台，明顯係草菅人命，忽視火警風險胡亂開槍。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B0%E6%AC%BE%E9%8E%AE%E5%A3%93%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99-%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%BD%88%E5%B7%B2%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%9C%B0%E4%BF%BE%E4%B9%9C%E9%87%8E%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%84%E4%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%258E%25AE%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25A3%259D%25E5%2582%2599-%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A-%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%2598%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BF%25BE%25E4%25B9%259C%25E9%2587%258E%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%2F&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiZa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=d67efa10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25A7%258B%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25